{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Regulate & require approval of non-standard modifications to road-going vehicles",
        "additional_details": "Vehicle modifications such as suspension lowering or geometry changes, stretching of tyres or using below acceptable quality parts can be dangerous.\r\n \r\nParts should be regulated and all modifications required to be inspected for safety.\r\nVehicles with unsafe modifications can cause injury or death. This needs to be regulated and monitored.",
        "background": "We believe modifications to vehicles are getting ridiculous & can be unsafe. The Government should take a similar approach to Germany & Australia and regulate use of non-standard parts, and require modifications to be inspected for roadworthiness. Stop unsafe and dangerous modifications!",
